> <em>Billboard</em> <strong><em><a  rel="noreferrer noopener"  target="_blank"  href="https://www.billboard.com/t/latin/"  >拉丁</a></em></strong><em>音乐周将于 10 月 14 日至 18 日重返迈阿密海滩，确认的超级巨星包括格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡 (Gloria Estefan)、亚历杭德罗·桑斯 (Alejandro Sanz) 和佩索·普拉玛 (Peso Pluma) 等。如需门票和更多详情，请访问</em><strong><em><a  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  target="_blank"  href="http://billboardlatinmusicweek.com/"  >Billboardlatinmusicweek.com</a></em></strong> <em>。</em></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235784684</post-id></item><item><title> ColourPop 进入颠倒局面：以下是购买“怪奇物语”系列的方法</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/culture/product-recommendations/colourpop-stranger-things-shop-the-collection-1235784587/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Latifah Muhammad]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:39:48 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Culture]]></category><category><![CDATA[Product Recommendations]]></category><category><![CDATA[beauty]]></category><category><![CDATA[culture]]></category><category><![CDATA[lifestyle]]></category><category><![CDATA[Product Reccommendations]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235784587 </guid><description><![CDATA[The ColourPop x Stranger Things collection drops on Sept. 26.  ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p class="pmc-ecomm-disclaimer">所有特色产品和服务均由编辑独立选择。然而，Billboard 可能会收到通过其零售链接下的订单的佣金，并且零售商可能会收到某些用于会计目的的可审计数据。</p><p class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "> <a rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://colourpop.sjv.io/c/256585/556522/9292?subId1=BB&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fcolourpop.com">ColourPop</a>正在以<a rel="noreferrer noopener sponsored" target="_blank" href="https://www.billboard.com/culture/product-recommendations/how-to-get-free-netflix-deals-promos-1235612004/">Netflix</a>剧集<em><a rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" href="https://